</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Independence_of_irrelevant_alternatives&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Independence_of_irrelevant_alternatives&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this article or section</a> by expanding it.</b> Further information might be found on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Independence_of_irrelevant_alternatives" title="Talk:Independence of irrelevant alternatives">talk page</a>. <small><i>(August 2007)</i></small></td>
